<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Status Transaksi</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family:
      'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; } table { border-collapse:
      collapse; width: 100%; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5;">

    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">

          <table
            border="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="100%"
            style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);"
          >

            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="background-color: #ef4444; padding: 30px 20px;"
              >
                <h1
                  style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;"
                >Transaksi Dibatalkan ‚ö†Ô∏è</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 30px 20px; color: #333333;">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Halo
                  <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>

                <p
                  style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;"
                >
                  Mohon maaf, kami menginformasikan bahwa transaksi
                  <strong>#{{transactionId}}</strong>
                  untuk event
                  <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>
                  tidak dapat kami proses (Ditolak/Kadaluarsa).
                </p>

                <div
                  style="background-color: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #10b981; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;"
                >
                  <p
                    style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #065f46;"
                  >üîÑ Pengembalian Dana & Voucher:</p>
                  <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #064e3b;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><strong>{{pointsUsed}}
                        Poin</strong>
                      telah dikembalikan ke saldo Anda.</li>
                    <li>Voucher
                      <strong>{{voucherCode}}</strong>
                      telah aktif kembali.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <p
                  style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 30px;"
                >
                  <em>Catatan: Reservasi kursi Anda telah dibatalkan. Jika Anda
                    masih ingin menghadiri event ini, silakan melakukan
                    pemesanan ulang segera.</em>
                </p>

              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="background-color: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;"
              >
                <p style="margin: 0;">¬©
                  {{currentYear}}
                  Eventify. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0 0;">Jika ini kesalahan, silakan hubungi
                  <a href="#" style="color: #ef4444;">Support kami</a>.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>

        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>